header.heading: SeanKrail.com
header.paragraph: My personal website running on Amazon Web Services' Elastic Beanstalk powered by Node.js with Express.

content.html:
My personal website

It runs on Amazon Web Services' (AWS) Elastic Beanstalk powered by Node.js with Express hosted by AWS Route 53 at seankrail.com. I host my resume and project portfolio on it. After having completed this website, I have a-whole-nother respect for frontend web developers.
